==English==
===Etymology===
from Latin ''[[conglobare]]'', ''[[conglobat-]]'', combinations of '[[com-]]'' ("[[together]]") + ''[[globus]]'' ("[[ball]]")
===Adjective===
'''conglobate'''
#[[shaped]] like a [[globe]] or [[ball]].
===Verb===
'''conglobate''' ''(transivite)''
#to form into a [[globe]] or [[ball]].